
|WKBSyntax: |YKBequip
 
|WKBDESCRIPTION
|WKO===========
 
|YKOThis command will quickly wear all your armour and wield your weapon.
Be warned though, it is not a foolproof way to get equiped with the
best of all your equipment you might be carrying.  After equipping,
make sure you are wearing and using the correct armours and weapons.
